{"tid":1162301,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"［買咗既自求多福］路透：google唔再同華為支援Android 更新","createTime":"2019-05-19T19:17:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T00:36:14.000Z","uid":48083,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"debb41bdafaf9266dbb59b2698fabe458e4db981","tid":1162301,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T19:17:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kvCbQfc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkvCbQfc.png&h=995953a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(續）<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\nHuawei Technologies Co Ltd will immediately lose access to updates to the Android operating system, and the next version of its smartphones outside of China will also lose access to popular applications and services including the Google Play Store and Gmail app.</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nDetails of the specific services were still being discussed internally at Google, according to the source. Huawei attorneys are also studying the impact of the U.S. Commerce Department&rsquo;s actions, a Huawei spokesman said on Friday. Huawei was not immediately reachable for further comment.<br />\n<br />\nRepresentatives of the U.S. Commerce Department did not immediately have comment.<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\nHuawei will continue to have access to the version of the Android operating system available through the open source license that is freely open to anyone who wishes to use it.</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\nBut Google will stop providing any technical support and collaboration for Android and Google services to Huawei going forward, the source said.</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nOn Thursday the Trump administration officially added Huawei to a trade blacklist, immediately enacting restrictions that will make it extremely difficult for the technology giant to do business with U.S. companies. [nL2N22S1RG]<br />\n<br />\nReporting by Angela Moon; Additional reporting by Georgina Prodhan in London, and David Shepardson and Karen Freifeld in Washington; Editing by Kenneth Li and Daniel Wallis<br />\n<a href=\"https://reut.rs/2w88OdK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Freut.rs%2F2w88OdK&d=3iEKCEnQ8TgOeM43nfYZ118MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=3cc539f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://reut.rs/2w88OdK</a>["},{"pid":"46904530e47c2de1cc1c0e2dd96abcb767f68c63","tid":1162301,"uid":12021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T19:31:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eb11d3354cdf0eab54a7de1b38f53d6f94b6809c","tid":1162301,"uid":58413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T19:51:58.000Z","msg":"即係仲可以用 android?"},{"pid":"5575daae0dc7df7781f1fc5958d0b339e6b4abf7","tid":1162301,"uid":3063,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"eb11d3354cdf0eab54a7de1b38f53d6f94b6809c","tid":1162301,"uid":58413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T19:51:58.000Z","msg":"即係仲可以用 android?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T19:53:31.000Z","msg":"去到某個版本<br />\n就好多app都用唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"957af97fe18967bf599bf22ec1f62d6ed81002c4","tid":1162301,"uid":78399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb11d3354cdf0eab54a7de1b38f53d6f94b6809c","tid":1162301,"uid":58413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T19:51:58.000Z","msg":"即係仲可以用 android?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T19:54:07.000Z","msg":"Android open source 但係google 每代個個升級就唔知係咪啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1714ca6e9490f1a2236f367f3b82b475f99b1ab","tid":1162301,"uid":63311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T19:54:54.000Z","msg":"自己刷lineage個d rom應該唔會有事<br />\n但係買得屎為個d邊識呢d<br />\n等做孤兒仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" cl